2651; (2006) Report of the Working Group on Acoustic and Egg Surveys for Sardine and Anchovy in ICES Areas VIII and IX, 24-28 October 2005, Vigo, Spain, p. 126. , ICES ICES CM 2006/LRC: 01; (2006) IUCN Red List of Threatened Species, , www.iucnredlist.org, IUCN; Josey, S.A., Kent, E.C., Taylor, P.K., New insights into the ocean heat budget closure problem from analysis of the SOC air-sea flux climatology (1999) J. Clim., 12, pp. 2856-2880. , doi:10.1175/1520-0442(1999)012!2856: NIITOHO2.0.CO;2; McMahon, C.R., Hays, G.C., Thermal niche, large-scale movements and implications of climate change for a critically endangered marine vertebrate (2006) Global Change Biol., 12, pp. 1330-1338. , doi:10.1111/j.1365-2486.2006.01174.x; Oro, D., Aguilar, J.S., Igual, J.M., Louazo, M., Modelling demography and extinction risk in the endangered Balearic shearwater (2004) Biol. Conserv., 116, pp. 93-102. , doi:10.1016/S0006-3207(03)00180-0; Parmesan, C., Yohe, G., A globally coherent fingerprint of climate change impacts across natural systems (2003) Nature, 421, pp. 37-42. , doi:10.1038/nature01286; Perry, A.L., Low, P.J., Ellis, J.R., Reynolds, J.D., Climate change and distribution shifts in marine fishes (2005) Science, 308, pp. 1912-1915. , doi:10.1126/science.1111322; Poulard, J.-C., Blanchard, F., The impact of climate change on the fish community structure of the eastern continental shelf of the Bay of Biscay (2005) ICES J. Mar. Sci., 62, pp. 1436-1443. , doi:10.1016/j.icesjms.2005.04.017; Rayner, N.A., Brohan, P., Parker, D.E., Folland, C.K., Kennedy, J.J., Vanicek, M., Ansell, T., Tett, S.F.B., Improved analyses of changes and uncertainties in sea surface temperature measured in situ since the mid-nineteenth century: The HadSST2 dataset (2006) J. Clim., 19, pp. 446-469. , doi:10.1175/JCLI3637.1; Reid, P.C., Edwards, M., Hunt, H.G., Warner, A.J., Phytoplankton change in the North Atlantic (1998) Nature, 391, p. 546. , doi:10.1038/35290; Richardson, A.J., Schoeman, D.S., Clima